description.narrative: This activity (International Secondments) is a component of FCDO Secondments to International Development Partners reported by FCDO, with a funding type of 'Multilateral organisation' and a budget of £16,017,574. This component benefits Developing countries, unspecified, and works in the following sector(s): Sectors not specified. , with the following implementing partners: Crown Agents Bank, Foreign, Commonwealth and Development Office, Organisation for Economic Co-operation and Development (OECD), United Nations Children's Fund (UNICEF), United Nations Population Fund (UNFPA). The start date is 01-11-2009 and the end date is 31-03-2021.
